product.name: Motion Sensor 13 Gallon 50 Liter Stainless Steel Odorless Slim Trash Can by Furniture of America
product.shortDescription: Keep your kitchen space clean and hygienic with this sleek silver trash can. The 13-gallon capacity provides ample room for disposing of household waste, while the convenient motion sensor lid ensures hands-free operation, minimizing contact and odors.
product.description:
Keep your kitchen space clean and hygienic with this sleek silver trash can. The 13-gallon capacity provides ample room for disposing of household waste, while the convenient motion sensor lid ensures hands-free operation, minimizing contact and odors. With an inner garbage bag ring to secure and hide the bag, this trash can combines functionality and modern design to seamlessly integrate into any room.

Features:
  • STAINLESS STEEL: High quality, rust-proof material avoids fingerprints and is waterproof
  • MOTION SENSOR: Touch-free infrared sensor keeps lid open for seven (7) seconds
  • SECURE BAG RING: Inner garbage bag ring keeps liner out of sight
  • Available in five (5) colors: Black, Blue, Red, Silver, White
  • Requires four (4) C batteries, not included
  • Simple modern design with stainless steel can
  • Anti-fouling and waterproof to resist corrosion and rust
  • Hands-free design is easy to clean and operate
  • Odorless design with tight top lid
  • Backside has a switch to convert automatic motion sensor to manual open mode
  • Includes handy latch on back of trash can to move or lift item
  • Non-slip base compatible with tile or wood flooring
  • No assembly needed

Dimensions:
  • Overall: 22.83 inches high x 15.75 inches wide x 11.14 inches deep
  • Capacity: 13.2 gallons / 50 liters
  • Weight: 7 lbs total

Whether you are a deal seeker, trendsetter or just window shopping, Furniture of America® is there for your every need. You'll find that we offer every style, from rustic farmhouse and urban industrial to french antique, mid-century modern, and glamorous chic; we welcome you to explore our ample style possibilities to find the perfect pairing for your personality. Furniture of America® is proud to be the family friend that always has your back.

Product Care: Wipe with a dry cloth.

This product will ship to you in one (1) box.

faceoff_positive.comments: Love this trash can, it's the perfect size to fit right where I need it to fit. I also love the sensor so you don't have to touch the top of the can to throw things out. Another good feature is if you have a lot to throw out you can press the open button and it will stay open until you press the close button.
faceoff_positive.headline: Perfect!!!

faceoff_negative.comments:
Hello, I cannot give this a higher rating because out of the box the lid did NOT work properly. The lid closed normally as it should but it would only open about an inch.

I decided to open it up. I don't build things, sure I set up furniture and some basic things. The fact that it wasn't working annoyed me so much, that I decided to open it up and watch the parts as I clicked it to open and close. Maybe I could then remove the batteries and try adjusting something.

What I found was that just unscrewing the whole thing, fixed it! Just like that. I didn't do anything but expose the mechanisms underneath and then I tried the open and close (kept the battery in at first just to try it and see the movement of parts) and it worked perfectly! So the issue must have been that the screws were on too tightly and somehow prohibited the proper opening of the lid. I screwed the two pieces back together, and made sure not to tighten them too much and it continues to work perfectly.

The manufacturer needs to test the lids after it's completely assembled to prevent shipping out lids with this problem.
faceoff_negative.headline: Lid not opening properly - Found a way to resolve
